{"name": "canonical-transformer", "metadata": {"name": "canonical-transformer", "version": "0.1.3", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": "https://github.com/nailen1/canonical_transformer.git", "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["numpy", "pandas", "python-dateutil", "pytz", "typing_extensions"], "summary": "A Python module for canonical data transformations between different data types and formats. Provides standardized mappings between DataFrames, dictionaries, files, and other data structures.", "upload_time": 1733925892}, "documentation": ["# Canonical Transformer\n\nA Python module for canonical data transformations between different data types and formats. Provides standardized mappings between DataFrames, dictionaries, files, and other data structures.\n\n## Features\n\n- DataFrame to Dictionary conversion\n- Dictionary to DataFrame conversion\n- DataFrame to CSV file transformation\n- CSV file to DataFrame loading\n- Standardized data type mapping\n- Simple and consistent API\n\n## Installation\n\n```bash\npip install canonical-transformer\n```\n\n## Quick Start\n\n```python\nfrom canonical_transformer import *\n\n# map DataFrame to dict\nmy_dict = map_df_to_data(my_dataframe)\n\n# map Dict to DataFrame\nresult_df = map_data_to_df(my_dict)\n\n# map DataFrame to CSV with standard format\nmap_df_to_csv(df=my_dataframe, file_folder='./', file_name='my_csv_file.csv')\n```\n\n## Requirements\n\n- Python >= 3.6\n- numpy >= 2.1.3\n- pandas >= 2.2.3\n- python-dateutil >= 2.9.0\n- pytz >= 2024.2\n- typing_extensions >= 4.12.2\n\n## License\n\nThis project is licensed under the MIT License - see the LICENSE file for details.\n\n## Contributing\n\nContributions are welcome! Please feel free to submit a Pull Request.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "canonical_transformer.dataframe_utils", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "canonical_transformer.dataframe_utils.map_df_to_data", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "df", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "capitalize", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "canonical_transformer.dataframe_utils.map_data_to_df", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "data", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "canonical_transformer", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "canonical_transformer.format_utils", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "canonical_transformer.format_utils.rename_columns", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "df", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "mapping", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "canonical_transformer.format_utils.capitalize_column_names_in_df", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "df", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "canonical_transformer.mapping_alias", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "canonical_transformer.mapping_alias.map_df_to_csv", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "canonical_transformer.mapping_alias.map_df_to_json", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "canonical_transformer.mapping_alias.map_data_to_json", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "canonical_transformer.save_utils", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "canonical_transformer.save_utils.save_df_as_csv", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "df", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "file_folder", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "file_name", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "canonical_transformer.save_utils.save_data_as_json", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "data", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "file_folder", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "file_name", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "canonical_transformer.save_utils.save_df_as_json", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "df", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "file_folder", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "file_name", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "canonical_transformer.xml_utils", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "canonical_transformer.xml_utils.map_xml_file_to_json", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "file_name_xml", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "file_folder", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "canonical_transformer.specialized_utils", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "canonical_transformer.specialized_utils.transfrom_df_to_data_fits_universal_dataframe", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "df", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "rnd", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "canonical_transformer.loader_utils", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "canonical_transformer.loader_utils.load_json_file", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "file_name", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}]}